1) You might need to install these dependencies first:
    apt-get install libnetcdf-dev libnetcdf-cxx-legacy-dev libblas-dev liblapack-dev

2) Make sure you have XSTG_ROOT and OCXXR_LIB_ROOT correctly set in your environment.
   See the ocxxr README for more details on those variables.

3) Run `make` in the root tempest directory to build the library.

4) cd test/hpc

5) make -f Makefile.x86 run
